description: Gets metadata information about the test execution.

parameters.name: testExecutionId
parameters.description: The execution Id of the test set execution.

nested_items.name: testExecutionId
nested_items.description: The execution Id for the test set execution.

nested_items.name: creationDateTime
nested_items.description: The execution creation date and time for the test set execution.

nested_items.name: lastUpdatedDateTime
nested_items.description: The date and time of the last update for the execution.

nested_items.name: testExecutionStatus
nested_items.description: The test execution status for the test execution.

nested_items.name: testSetId
nested_items.description: The test set Id for the test set execution.

nested_items.name: testSetName
nested_items.description: The test set name of the test set execution.

nested_items.name: botAliasTarget
nested_items.description: Contains information about the bot alias used for the test execution.

nested_items.name: botId
nested_items.description: The bot Id of the bot alias used in the test set execution.

nested_items.name: botAliasId
nested_items.description: The bot alias Id of the bot alias used in the test set execution.

nested_items.name: localeId
nested_items.description: The locale Id of the bot alias used in the test set execution.

nested_items.name: apiMode
nested_items.description: Indicates whether we use streaming or non-streaming APIs are used for the test set execution. For streaming, StartConversation Amazon Lex Runtime API is used. Whereas for non-streaming, RecognizeUtterance and RecognizeText Amazon Lex Runtime API is used.

nested_items.name: testExecutionModality
nested_items.description: Indicates whether test set is audio or text.

nested_items.name: failureReasons
nested_items.description: Reasons for the failure of the test set execution.
